<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.7.3">
<l>maṉṉumā nilaṉum malaikaḷuṅ kaṭalum vāṉamum tāṉava rulakum</l>
<l>tuṉṉumā yiruḷāyt tulaṅkoḷi curuṅkit tollaināṉ maṟaikaḷum maṟaiya</l>
<l>piṉṉumvā ṉavarkkum muṉivark kunalkip piṟaṅkiruḷ niṟaṅkeṭa vorunāḷ</l>
<l>aṉṉamā yaṉṟaṅ karumaṟai payantā ṉaraṅkamā nakaramarn tāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who lies calmly in the great city of Araṅkam</l>
<l rend="indent">is he who produced the precious Vedas,</l>
<l>Bestowing [them] again to celestials and sages,</l>
<l rend="indent">then and there as a swan one day,</l>
<l>When he destroyed the color of the spreading darkness –</l>
<l rend="indent">the massive eternal earth, mountains, seas, heavens,</l>
<l rend="indent">the world of the Dānavas,</l>
<l>Becoming a great thick darkness [and] bright lights diminishing -</l>
<l rend="indent">when the four ancient Vedas were hidden.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
